ring-even-one-daughter-bint\/","url_meta":{"origin":24178,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Daughters: He will enter Paradise if he cares for even one","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 15, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Jabir ibn Abdullah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever has three daughters and he cares for them, he is merciful to them, and he clothes them, then Paradise is certainly required\u00a0for him.\u201d It was said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, what if he has\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":920,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/07\/13\/taking-care-daughters-paradise\/","url_meta":{"origin":24178,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Family: Taking care of daughters leads to Paradise","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 13, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \"There is no Muslim with two daughters, caring for them in the best manner as long as he accompanies them, but that they will admit him into Paradise.\" Source: Musnad\u00a0Ah\u0323mad 3414 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Ahmad Shakir \u0639\u0646 \u0627\u0628\u0646\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":87,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2010\/10\/26\/caring-for-daughters-young-girls\/","url_meta":{"origin":24178,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Women: 